Katie stopped by to give the Whole30 community some much needed uplift during #mentalhealthawarenessmonth! 

PLUS - she talked us through creating two tabs - joy + connection - to help us gauge when we need a little more love, space, and time for ourselves, and when we need to be giving to others.

She also created some freebie worksheets to help all of you maintain your mental health - you can find them at womenagainstnegativetalk.com — LOOK FOR FREEBIES!

#knowyourendo #endometriosisawareness #jessicamurnane #womenshealth

Are you joining us for the September Whole30? Drop a ✋🏿✋🏾✋🏽✋🏼✋🏻 in the comments if you’re in! The #SeptemberWhole30 starts on Wednesday, 9/1. It’s an annual tradition for our community to take a beat in September to reset and recenter. (Most of us) aren’t going back to school, yet September still feels like an opportunity to start anew—with our health, habits, and relationship with food; with meal planning and meal prep routines; and by focusing on foods that support great sleep, renewed energy, glowing skin and more.

We are honored to lead you through the September Whole30, and have created a slate of resources to help you succeed.

📝Our entire program is free (and always will be). It’s available to download right from our website, along with other free resources.

📧Our exclusive September Whole30 emails are a free, informative and encouraging weekly email series. We only send these to people who REALLY want them, so you have to sign up for them even if you already get our emails. 

📚The Whole30 books and cookbooks are fundamental Whole30 resources. Check out THE WHOLE30 for everything you need to know plus 100 delicious recipes, and THE WHOLE30 DAY BY DAY for daily check-ins, pep talks, and opportunities to journal and reflect on your experience.

🤳Daily text messages from @melissau guide you through your Whole30 day by day, with timely messages from our CEO herself. The Whole30 text messaging subscription is $14.99.

💪Our Whole30 Certified Coaches offer a range of group and one-on-one Coaching options. This is a fun way to tackle the September Whole30 with a smaller community of people and work with a Coach who can quickly and accurately address specific issues you encounter. Pricing and schedule varies.

This is a great time to turn on notifications as we’ll be rolling out new resources and making exciting announcements in the next few weeks. (Tap to our profile page, tap the 🔔 in the upper right hand corner, and then select the notifications you’d like to receive.) We look forward to September all year long and can not wait to support you during your #SeptemberWhole30
